message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as the paper deals with speech enhancement using deep networks. Other likely categories could be cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.SY, and cs.CL. cs.LG because the paper uses deep learning techniques, cs.SI because it evaluates the performance using scale-invariant signal-to-distortion ratio (SI-SDR), cs.SY because it deals with signal processing, and cs.CL because it deals with speech processing.
